\emph on
The Impact of El Nino-Southern Oscillation on Agricultural Stock Returns
\emph default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 that was submitted to Ecological Economics in 2018.
 First off, let me express my sincere gratitude to you for sending the paper
 out for review, and for the comments from the reviewers.
 While the paper was rejected, you gave me the opportunity to revise and
 resubmit the paper as a new submission.
 We have revised the paper, and addressed all the concerns raised by both
 reviewers, and are resubmitting the paper as a new submission for consideration
 for publication in Ecological Economics.
